Former American president Bill Clinton has teamed up with one of Americas greatest writers James Patterson to write a book, NYTimes writes. Come June 2018, Alfred A. Knopf and Little, Brown and Company will produce and publish the book titled The President Is Missing. The intriguing novel is a “unique amalgam of intrigue, suspense and behind-the-scenes global drama” that will be “informed by insider details that only a president can know”, the company stated. Did i hear you say greatness?